BOLSWESSANEN TO BUY U . S . FOOD GROUP . Dutch food and drinks concern BolsWessanen NV said on Tuesday it would acquire the U . S . group Specialty Foods Distributors . The cost of the transaction , to be completed by cash settlement within a month , was not disclosed . " Agreement has been reached on the acquisition of Specialty Foods Distributors Inc by Tree of Life , ( BolWessanen ' s U . S . distribution operation ) , " BolsWessanen said in a statement . It said Specialty Foods , based in Plant City , Florida , was a leading distributor of delicatessen and regional spcialities in the south east of the United States with an annual turnover of some 190 million guilders . - - Amsterdam Newsroom + 31 20 504 5000 
